exercises.name: Single String Scale
exercises.description: Play the desired scale up and down the neck on a single string using different finger groupings. Say the notes aloud as you play them.

exercises.name: Contrary Motion
exercises.description: While working within a scale, grab the lowest and the highest possible notes in position. Then  work up and down the scale in contrary motion using double stops.

notes.note: Struggle but became comfortable at higher speeds
